  "/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Fabric.Admin/fabricLocations/{location}/fileShares":
    get:
      description: Returns a list of all fabric file shares at a certain location.
      operationId: FileShares_List
      parameters:
        - description: Subscription credentials that uniquely identify Microsoft Azure
            subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every
            service call.
          in: path
          name: subscriptionId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
          examples:
            Returns a list of all fabric file shares at a certain location.:
              value: 20ff7fc3-e762-44dd-bd96-b71116dcdc23
        - description: Name of the resource group.
          in: path
          name: resourceGroupName
          required: true
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
          examples:
            Returns a list of all fabric file shares at a certain location.:
              value: System.local
        - description: Location of the resource.
          in: path
          name: location
          required: true
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
          examples:
            Returns a list of all fabric file shares at a certain location.:
              value: local
        - description: Client API Version.
          in: query
          name: api-version
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            default: 2016-05-01
          examples:
            Returns a list of all fabric file shares at a certain location.:
              value: 2016-05-01
        - description: OData filter parameter.
          in: query
          name: $filter
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/FileShareList"
              examples:
                Returns a list of all fabric file shares at a certain location.:
                  $ref: "#/components/examples/Returns_a_list_of_all_fabric_file_sh\
                    ares_at_a_certain_location."
        "404":
          description: NOT FOUND
      tags:
        - FileShares
      x-ms-odata: "#/components/schemas/FileShare"
      x-ms-pageable: {}
  "/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Fabric.Admin/fabricLocations/{location}/fileShares/{fileShare}":
    get:
      description: Returns the requested fabric file share.
      operationId: FileShares_Get
      parameters:
        - description: Subscription credentials that uniquely identify Microsoft Azure
            subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every
            service call.
          in: path
          name: subscriptionId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
          examples:
            Returns the requested fabric file share.:
              value: 20ff7fc3-e762-44dd-bd96-b71116dcdc23
        - description: Name of the resource group.
          in: path
          name: resourceGroupName
          required: true

            type: string
          examples:
            Returns the requested fabric file share.:
              value: System.local
        - description: Location of the resource.
          in: path
          name: location
          required: true
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
          examples:
            Returns the requested fabric file share.:
              value: local
        - $ref: "#/components/parameters/FileShareParameter"
        - description: Client API Version.
          in: query
          name: api-version
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            default: 2016-05-01
          examples:
            Returns the requested fabric file share.:
              value: 2016-05-01
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/FileShare"
              examples:
                Returns the requested fabric file share.:
                  $ref: "#/components/examples/Returns_the_requested_fabric_file_sh\
                    are."
        "404":
          description: NOT FOUND
      tags:
        - FileShares
